description:
THIS IS STILL A WORK IN PROGRESS!  Everything is in, but might be a little buggy!

A Stroll Through Anatidae State Park

In a daring mood you decided to take a boat out to closed Anatidae State park, who cares about the stories of missing people, and rumors of monsters!

There are 5 different endings for your journey through the park!

Made for the Bitsy Jam! This time the theme is Duck!

Adam Le Doux - For making Bitsy in the first place! 

Ruin - For the  Pixy tool when enables me to do what I do.
